high_descs: walk to face bath tub
pick up candle stick from tub edge
turn to face bureau to the left of the tub
put the candle stick in bottom left bureau drawer
walk to face top of bureau
pick up candle stick from top of bureau
walk back to face bureau drawers
put the candle stick in bottom left bureau drawer
anns.task_desc: put two candle sticks in bureau drawer

high_descs: Turn around to walk towards the bathtub.
Pick up the candlestick on the ledge of the bathtub.
Turn to face the drawers on the left.
Put the candlestick into the leftmost, lower drawer.
Turn to face the top of the drawers.
Pick up the rightmost candlestick on top of the drawers.
Turn to face the drawers on the left.
Put the other candlestick into the leftmost, lower drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two candlesticks away in the leftmost, lower drawer.

high_descs: turn around and move to the bath tub
pick up the bottle of nail polish that is on the ledge of the bath tub
turn to the left to face the counter that is to the left of the bath tub
open the bottom drawer that is the second from the left, put the bottle of nail polish in to the drawer and close it
move to face the right side of the counter
pick up the bottle of nail polish that is in the back right corner of the counter
move to the left side of the counter
open the second from the left bottom drawer, put the second bottle of nail polish to the right of the first bottle and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: put two bottles of nail polish in to the drawer
